    "Further information regarding the training and evaluation process can be found in the Appendix A.",
    "Like Section 4.2, we train an SFT model using the UltraChat dataset.",
    "Additionally, we employ UltraFeedback to train the pre-trained model with alignment methods, as described in scenario 1.",
